name: ipcalc
description:
This is a modern tool to assist in network address calculations for IPv4
and IPv6. It acts both as a tool to output human readable information
about a network or address, as well as a tool suitable to be used by
scripts or other programs.

dependencies.name: geoip-api-c
dependencies.description:
The GeoIP Legacy C library enables the user to find geographical and
network information of an IP address.
